After saving money, what is the plan for "after 90"?
Alipay data shows that "after 90" has the habit of saving money for the goal, and the users who take travel as the goal of saving money are the most numerous.
As a result of the pandemic, many "post-90s" have saved money to prepare for post-pandemic travel; the resumption of cinemas has also provided a new way to shift from saving money to spending.
