"The scales of the fish caught are black, and the inside is black after being cut open."
Li Daiguo said that it is more and more difficult to fish after the river is polluted.
Local efforts have been made to control the pollution of Longxi River, including drifting, river patrolling and aquatic resources management.
Li Daiguo also switched from fishing to production and became a member of the river patrol team to protect the aquatic resources.
