How does director Dapeng face this "providence" and how should he continue to meet the changes brought about by this providence?
There is no doubt that "Good luck" is full of experimentation. The almost all-vegan cast and innovative audio-visual style turn life in front of the camera into a movie. Wrapped in real images, the audience will also find themselves and their families' shadows from the families presented in the film. With the conclusion of this family gathering in the film, it evokes a series of reflections.
